NT version 0.01
===============

This module provides a perl interface into Win32 objects for systems
management. It is intended for use with FTMON.
You will need Visual C++ and the SDK Platform from Microsoft for (psapi).
INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   nmake
   nmake test
   nmake install

To copy the NT library to the correct place in a FTMON distribution run
	install_lib.cmd

To compile the FTMON eventlog messages
	compile_messages.cmd

To install the FTMON messages
	install_messages.cmd



DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:
	psapi
	pdh

